":310740,"uid":59919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T08:07:55.000Z","msg":"台仔比屎佢食教話好食<br />\n上次去歐洲跟台仔blog佢話好出名嘅食飯<br />\n又貴又唔好食<br />\n我求其係街搵間行入去都好食過佢介紹果d"},{"pid":"e7b1d08f13d7e809369cfad56abecb9f39fc6fbe","tid":310740,"uid":34503,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T08:12:15.000Z","msg":"你睇下台仔推介去香港食咩先講"},{"pid":"0063964c5cabdbb1d169ae8390ca402c11adce1d","tid":310740,"uid":120068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T08:12:34.000Z","msg":"屌 終於有大講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n台灣d blogger真係大伏"},{"pid":"e07f112930092402aab5739741a4d29873a93270","tid":310740,"uid":57962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T08:15:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3b4a1807a2343fd2fc5322bd5839d129f0504ba7","tid":310740,"uid":122867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T08:16:56.000Z","msg":"極同意<br />\n佢地咩都話好食 <br />\n傻傻地"},{"pid":"0feb89b0bb0d2491957cd1ab62b5dad67f513c8e","tid":310740,"uid":57827,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T08:17:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不嬲台仔blog只有交通可以信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n交通都唔應該信<br />\n唔知係咪智商問題, 行兩步轉兩程車都講到登陸月球咁困難"},{"pid":"389a35c6b73f2f81c437d1f49b1b1dc96c0b78d6","tid":310740,"uid":39084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T08:18:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>台灣人食開屎，去過台灣都應該知</blockquote><br />\n台灣人唔識分咩叫食得落口同好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fc95fd591c2b57d1ab2aab9c15011a084173245","tid":310740,"uid":33357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T08:28:46.000Z","msg":"pixnet<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f62c4682dfbb9e4111e773ef4d77e1ad3c9ef401","tid":310740,"uid":74192,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T08:32:28.000Z","msg":"台blog都有高質野食既<br />\n不過要做好多搜集同比較<br />\n<br />\n之前睇台仔blog食大幸 拉麵唔錯"},{"pid":"ea6b9646d1f7ca02d6a13cbe7ca071651f1a9fc7","tid":310740,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T08:36:50.000Z","msg":"前幾日睇電視唔知邊個台 台灣豬黎到香港中環長洲食埋啲普通野叫哂春咁 香港機人都知其實跟本無咁好食"},{"pid":"c96a36792bbbb05885bb2ad57309444bd3bc8800","tid":310740,"uid":1557,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T08:39:02.000Z","msg":"你睇吓台仔平時食乜<br />\n就知點解佢哋覺得咁驚艷<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63efe704cb4bc857a785b40ada8dbc9a4828581e","tid":310740,"uid":71175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T08:39:40.000Z","msg":"ic"},{"pid":"9722d25e86d8107c054b53d861e500c5a6e92626","tid":310740,"uid":71175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T08:40:08.000Z","msg":"資訊性係ok ge<br />\n<br />\n飲食不了"},{"pid":"4e1d6d72de1feefd333ee6928cb24c04f25f5ce6","tid":310740,"uid":40885,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T08:40:36.000Z","msg":"我係歐洲自由行兩個月都係靠台仔台妹blog<br />\n基本上交通可以盡信<br />\n不過唔係站站都有資料<br />\n同行日本仔話日本blog資料仲豐富<br />\n食物方面通常係睇佢地介紹當地特色食物<br />\n有咩必食小吃美食之類<br />\n但餐廳都係會睇google maps既留言（通常都幾準）<br />\n<br />\nBtw 根據同行台妹反應，佢真係乜都會覺得好食<br />\n有次信左台灣blog係Amsterdam 食媽媽餐廳<br />\nTraditional Dutch food<br />\n鹹到仆街仲要成廿歐一個人<br />\n除左鹹之外我咩都食唔出（日本仔同反應）<br />\n但台妹覺得好好食...<br />\n<br />\n有時希望香港人都會寫travel blog"},{"pid":"52c48b7c82119889b253a78d214cd6f8f98bc2c9","tid":310740,"uid":13257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T08:41:18.000Z","msg":"台灣blog介紹野食係完全信唔過"},{"pid":"191060fbf5ad692bd1c97eb95d7b9a339cb2362f","tid":310740,"uid":28245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T08:43:59.000Z","msg":"想講好耐 台狗未見過大蛇屙尿 乜撚都過超正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a42f876babf92c4fcabe7e4f2ff7435afa315b89","tid":310740,"uid":41411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T08:44:24.000Z","msg":"台灣blog最實際係交通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ed4f124f16d678fa1d34aea37f0c9b46e44941e","tid":310740,"uid":41411,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T08:45:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我係歐洲自由行兩個月都係靠台仔台妹blog<br />\n基本上交通可以盡信<br />\n不過唔係站站都有資料<br />\n同行日本仔話日本blog資料仲豐富<br />\n食物方面通常係睇佢地介紹當地特色食物<br />\n有咩必食小吃美食之類<br />\n但餐廳都係會睇google maps既留言（通常都幾準）<br />\n<br />\nBtw 根據同行台妹反應，佢真係乜都會覺得好食<br />\n有次信左台灣blog係Amsterdam 食媽媽餐廳<br />\nTraditional Dutch food<br />\n鹹到仆街仲要成廿歐一個人<br />\n除左鹹之外我咩都食唔出（日本仔同反應）<br />\n但台妹覺得好好食...<br />\n<br />\n有時希望香港人都會寫travel blog</blockquote><br />\n香港人大部分都隨性d 唔鍾意做咁多資料搜集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68c64a1ebe36a7aff45a95415523161e065fbd89","tid":310740,"uid":33730,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T08:48:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我係歐洲自由行兩個月都係靠台仔台妹blog<br />\n基本上交通可以盡信<br />\n不過唔係站站都有資料<br />\n同行日本仔話日本blog資料仲豐富<br />\n食物方面通常係睇佢地介紹當地特色食物<br />\n有咩必食小吃美食之類<br />\n但餐廳都係會睇google maps既留言（通常都幾準）<br />\n<br />\nBtw 根據同行台妹反應，佢真係乜都會覺得好食<br />\n有次信左台灣blog係Amsterdam 食媽媽餐廳<br />\nTraditional Dutch food<br />\n鹹到仆街仲要成廿歐一個人<br />\n除左鹹之外我咩都食唔出（日本仔同反應）<br />\n但台妹覺得好好食...<br />\n<br />\n有時希望香港人都會寫travel blog</blockquote><br />\n香港人大部分都隨性d 唔鍾意做咁多資料搜集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個個趕頭趕命咁, 點會有心機寫blog<br />\n寧願快快手放哂fb呃like好過啦..."},{"pid":"87f60a5df6305ee4a5740f03b1b80a1e30b081f6","tid":310740,"uid":12827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T08:53:16.000Z","msg":"佢地講野一向誇張<br />\n總之人生僅有美味、回台仲念念不忘=算好食<br />\n超好食=普通"},{"pid":"97056eb9bf6c02a724c42930f86eba8ee51d07c3","tid":310740,"uid":23897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"