0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T08:59:34.000Z","msg":"台灣blogger食開屎<br />\n<br />\n去沖繩食左2間介紹講到好撚好食既燒肉, 難撚食到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54bbfdf2cce33428c7c02aca0481d6e0605a1019","tid":310740,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T09:00:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3cc99ba64e283ef169c14760f856649217074b65","tid":310740,"uid":12827,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T09:00:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我係歐洲自由行兩個月都係靠台仔台妹blog<br />\n基本上交通可以盡信<br />\n不過唔係站站都有資料<br />\n同行日本仔話日本blog資料仲豐富<br />\n食物方面通常係睇佢地介紹當地特色食物<br />\n有咩必食小吃美食之類<br />\n但餐廳都係會睇google maps既留言（通常都幾準）<br />\n<br />\nBtw 根據同行台妹反應，佢真係乜都會覺得好食<br />\n有次信左台灣blog係Amsterdam 食媽媽餐廳<br />\nTraditional Dutch food<br />\n鹹到仆街仲要成廿歐一個人<br />\n除左鹹之外我咩都食唔出（日本仔同反應）<br />\n但台妹覺得好好食...<br />\n<br />\n有時希望香港人都會寫travel blog</blockquote><br />\n香港人大部分都隨性d 唔鍾意做咁多資料搜集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個個趕頭趕命咁, 點會有心機寫blog<br />\n寧願快快手放哂fb呃like好過啦...</blockquote><br />\n其實旅遊台好多blog都好高汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只係打出黎無台灣blogger咁多實際資訊<br />\n但講體驗文化既話香港高質d</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nAgger<br />\n而且有心寫既巴打都好多<br />\n做既野又特別d唔係倒模"},{"pid":"837b47c8f918dcb049cc4cd381c54ffa1ef168c0","tid":310740,"uid":12827,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T09:01:55.000Z","msg":"其實支那blog仲可信過台灣人<br />\n好多成日出去玩既支那人都叫有點見識<br />\n不過要忍受簡體字"},{"pid":"f55686bfc8b702993b2df62e8bf2de85c6cf86a6","tid":310740,"uid":79979,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T09:03:04.000Z","msg":"台灣人出國食嘢豬餿當魚翅是常識吧<br />\n利申：有唔少台灣朋友<br />\n<br />\n從來出國食嘢唔睇任何介紹<br />\n包括任何blog, 鳩假期，旅遊書<br />\n淨係求其行到邊食到邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e2f5c0d14722586f683cecee2292d55084f719b","tid":310740,"uid":19762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T09:03:56.000Z","msg":"我成日思疑台灣佬寫呢啲網誌有辦法幫佢哋搵到錢<br />\n係咪Google Ad有得分架"},{"pid":"6c5f0074fe28d04c2e05b7fb460c93adec69dced","tid":310740,"uid":1367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T09:05:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>台灣blog資料幾實用既<br />\n直接skip左食果part就得<br />\n有建樹過港豬只識打卡鳩威<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nAgger<br />\nSearch 酒店好有用<br />\n佢地影得勁detail <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nAgger"},{"pid":"bd7424d7f1ddb33dcacb738a4e2fa89d2a0dc374","tid":310740,"uid":12297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T09:07:06.000Z","msg":"台灣D blog資訊好齊好update<br />\n但介紹飲食嗰D真係好多都伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中過幾次伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家靠自己直覺算<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c6340ab3403789ac57d589e9b396e3b860b8f0f","tid":310740,"uid":30478,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T09:11:24.000Z","msg":"不嬲都係求其撞入去食<br />\n<br />\n最緊要係非遊客區，見好多日本人都食就實冇死"},{"pid":"b777883f39520add53c3dfaac98b5b640e2fa8aa","tid":310740,"uid":33730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T09:13:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我成日思疑台灣佬寫呢啲網誌有辦法幫佢哋搵到錢<br />\n係咪Google Ad有得分架</blockquote><br />\n搵錢就梗架喇, Blog入面好多廣告<br />\n可能台灣人得閒d, 有時間靠呢d去搵錢掛..."},{"pid":"a0ed8f78bf5a3fcb0efad58841d683a5533554b8","tid":310740,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T09:13:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實支那blog仲可信過台灣人<br />\n好多成日出去玩既支那人都叫有點見識<br />\n不過要忍受簡體字</blockquote><br />\n唔係ma,  支那blog成日介紹外地食中菜喎，<br />\n心諗去到外國都食中菜係咪有病"},{"pid":"821f26ecc91589d43ad68668342e5e2b72dba603","tid":310740,"uid":13257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T09:14:11.000Z","msg":"台灣根本無咩好食，出到去稍為好食d就讚到上天"},{"pid":"693f7dae04075337b01181296743b5992b290435","tid":310740,"uid":68146,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T09:15:07.000Z","msg":"台灣人形容親所有嘢都誇撚張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知係見得少定係個人無墨水，<br />\n唔只遊記睇完好似無睇過咁<br />\n啲影評寫撚到好似佢先係導演咁 生安白造 亂鳩咁黎 仲要扮專家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n現實識啲台灣人都係咁 因為比較少見識？<br />\n出過國同有錢當然唔同 不過間唔中會彈過唔make sense嘅冷知識出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但台灣人人品普遍係幾好就真</span>"},{"pid":"e621590a906a4faa87f067895d979702b5d70824","tid":310740,"uid":12900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T09:16:02.000Z","msg":"正常 台狗平時食慣垃圾"},{"pid":"523d572be8f5e98075f32017f925632c591de33c","tid":310740,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T09:16:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>香港人寫個啲咪一樣一擔擔 成個東亞比較睇得下<br />\n得日本仔啲blog <br />\n其他大部份都係廢嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港人好多時中左伏真係會屌<br />\n台灣人中伏都講到特別經驗好有樂趣</blockquote><br />\n香港人出名閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中咗伏仲介紹就真係收咗錢啦<br />\n有時連收咗錢都會彈（可能扮持平），或者啲字眼都輕力啲，輕描淡寫，起碼睇完你都有心理準備<br />\n但台灣人？一個彈嘅字都唔會有，你去到只會完美中伏。因為台灣人出文重點只係晒佢有去過，好撚開心好撚enjoy<br />\n你見台灣人話嚟香港嘅blog唔會話香港人閪，但你同台灣人傾，佢十個有九個都話嚟香港遇到嘅待遇唔好"},{"pid":"fe5964933f344eb015aeeb0f4b88ff4c6d7939b6","tid":310740,"uid":78253,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T09:16:47.000Z","msg":"搵美食嚟講<br />\n台灣blog可信度60%<br />\n窮撚出國嘛梗係乜都話好食<br />\n未見過話唔好食<br />\n同日本嚟講嘅難食都有個譜<br />\n<br />\n香港OpXXRXXe<br />\n好食可信度30%<br />\n難食可信度80%<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd7d127e15a714fdaaf02e769e39cc0e397f5ebd","tid":310740,"uid":38077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T09:31:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>用tabelog啦</blockquote><br />\n仲有Retty <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上個禮拜去名古屋都係用tabelog<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28833704c2f33907b06e52b4a0e8911624845c75","tid":310740,"uid":79979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T09:36:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不嬲都係求其撞入去食<br />\n<br />\n最緊要係非遊客區，見好多日本人都食就實冇死</blockquote><br />\n正解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果識日文，可以去冇圖冇真相menu餐廳食<br />\n大把好嘢食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13f5f2c03692c216765af183662947cc03a4e9a6","tid":310740,"uid":28472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T09:41:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>諗起喺新加玻俾人推到神檯嘅<span style=\"color: red;\">天天</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只可以話OK 但又未去到好好食</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47c29dfa785938871d7042f7abb31c21b399912f","tid":310740,"uid":36300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T09:44:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>諗起喺新加玻俾人推到神檯嘅<span style=\"color: red;\">天天</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只可以話OK 但又未去到好好食</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同鳩假期一樣，求鳩其推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"858660accacdbaf76155eb4bf480ade8ec333a27","tid":310740,"uid":36044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T09:45:05.000Z","msg":"仲有唔好睇愛評網<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4369204ef9f0a587de426c9534e73574c0e8580e","tid":310740,"uid":28472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T09:47:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實支那blog仲可信過台灣人<br />\n好多成日出去玩既支那人都叫有點見識<br />\n不過要忍受簡體字</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢樣真<br />\n支那網資訊多同埋準確得多<br />\n不過殘體囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f486e9fb34d928ba66b566ab18bad192e7a745cd","tid":310740,"uid":53811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T09:49:50.000Z","msg":"d步速都唔好信，台仔話要45分鐘行的路，我15分鐘行完，仲要影左幾十張相"},{"pid":"fd14c8a437e652daa926a154110994d74a68e2e9","tid":310740,"uid":119157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T09:50:35.000Z","msg":"睇台灣人blog淨係睇交通就夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48b286da2413744a3504fe304b96425600174914","tid":310740,"uid":28472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T09:50:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>諗起喺新加玻俾人推到神檯嘅<span style=\"color: red;\">天天</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只可以話OK 但又未去到好好食</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同鳩假期一樣，求鳩其推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我放一啖入口已經得啖笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"739e436a375bd95858fa3519e1a5f9aaf1604b4d","tid":310740,"uid":28472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T09:51:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實支那blog仲可信過台灣人<br />\n好多成日出去玩既支那人都叫有點見識<br />\n不過要忍受簡體字</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢樣真<br />\n支那網資訊多同埋準確得多<br />\n不過殘體囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講漏左<br />\n除左食之外<br />\n食野都係睇番TripAdvisor"},{"pid":"905fde3ceba2e1d2d1c14f9a33829ad7c0bfeca3","tid":310740,"uid":28472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T09:52:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇台灣人blog淨係睇交通就夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n交通係幾好既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有次意大利都係靠個blog 先搵到個火車站"},{"pid":"cc91e14d82ee4a21a9cee5338bff656653a1d489","tid":310740,"uid":33058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T09:53:56.000Z","msg":"台灣d人好撚on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n見個個blog乜鳩都寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n早幾個禮拜去歐洲搵交通<br />\n搵到幾個台灣blog<br />\n<br />\n佢話架車8:52開但佢話佢自己原來睇錯時間係8:25，去到月台仲問鳩人做咩開左架車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有個又係on9, 話見到隔離個韓國佬唔落車 以為未到，跟住冇落到車，以為果個地方應該係大站，自己發現要落既時候拖喼沖落去棟門閂左。要等下一個站等勁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n食果度又係<br />\n來到xxxx, 不得不吃xxxx，不然旅行幹嘛<br />\n睇到呢個就反感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>唯一得交通方法可信，資料自己要update下</strong></span>"},{"pid":"095b4d1c792ed0e1fc9b6fc1daba980abb47b352","tid":310740,"uid":74002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T09:58:36.000Z","msg":"佢地寫景點 酒店又幾詳細既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但10個有9個 篇篇都一定用映入眼簾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4563a94474d4b1443b7b40cc0a5c0bbf24729725","tid":310740,"uid":45353,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T10:01:01.000Z","msg":"香港剩老點<br />\n支那又殘體<br />\n日文唔識睇<br />\n鬼佬又味殘<br />\n<br />\n到頭黎睇台灣參考好過無"},{"pid":"1d8582bdbf6f2dc2e5a54c9888609ca715492320","tid":310740,"uid":36968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T10:02:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實支那blog仲可信過台灣人<br />\n好多成日出去玩既支那人都叫有點見識<br />\n不過要忍受簡體字</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢樣真<br />\n支那網資訊多同埋準確得多<br />\n不過殘體囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講漏左<br />\n除左食之外<br />\n食野都係睇番TripAdvisor</blockquote><br />\ntrip advisor 我都覺得唔係好準 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n例如日本菜 可能外國人未食過真正好味嘅日本菜"},{"pid":"9f43b79ca67503d5d953e14f99048247ea5ff1b8","tid":310740,"uid":17516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T10:07:51.000Z","msg":"食野真係垃圾到唔恨<br />\n之前介紹個麵話好足料<br />\n真係食個時好足料原來係指有好多種菜<br />\n肉呀其他野少到唔知食過"},{"pid":"910df6986cf62dd1494b9e3b6740b96be9a7e466","tid":310740,"uid":28472,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T10:11:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實支那blog仲可信過台灣人<br />\n好多成日出去玩既支那人都叫有點見識<br />\n不過要忍受簡體字</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢樣真<br />\n支那網資訊多同埋準確得多<br />\n不過殘體囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講漏左<br />\n除左食之外<br />\n食野都係睇番TripAdvisor</blockquote><br />\ntrip advisor 我都覺得唔係好準 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n例如日本菜 可能外國人未食過真正好味嘅日本菜</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁老老豆豆<br />\n假如係意大利<br />\n你想搵好食既日本菜/廣東菜<br />\n<br />\nTripAdvisor 當然可信性低好多<br />\n學你咁講<br />\n<br />\n佢地根本未食過好食既"},{"pid":"5c6f0c68db7eb6d345b90b6c71ece1c05162aba4","tid":310740,"uid":53254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T10:18:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實支那blog仲可信過台灣人<br />\n好多成日出去玩既支那人都叫有點見識<br />\n不過要忍受簡體字</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢樣真<br />\n支那網資訊多同埋準確得多<br />\n不過殘體囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講漏左<br />\n除左食之外<br />\n食野都係睇番TripAdvisor</blockquote><br />\n支那人咩都話唔好笑<br />\n服務差<br />\n份量少<br />\n<br />\n佢地都話好嘅多數真係好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26a40a26f22ddaa73a0b69ab4e4a2ea379e474d4","tid":310740,"uid":49220,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T10:26:33.000Z","msg":"屌, 網上資料咩都唔可以盡信架啦on9, 你個腦要黎生草架?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n起碼人地有資料丫, 而且都係大部份可信, 慘撚得過香港人?<br />\n香港有d乜撚貢獻啊? 出埋d垃圾閃閃旅遊書,<br />\n<br />\n以前我去旅行, 試過有次係高登分享心得資料,<br />\n有幾條on9 (唔係1個, 係幾個)留言問我分享黎做乜,<br />\n有錢賺架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7ed9898e07d769ad8eb761a82c6ac8c4948180f","tid":310740,"uid":17211,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T10:28:11.000Z","msg":"台狗不意外"},{"pid":"ef167f3a56d06ab2f9e3ce8f911af6171a802001","tid":310740,"uid":50500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T10:38:56.000Z","msg":"你去過台灣就知點解佢地咁崇日"},{"pid":"3b158730e0af80407027cdea434d48d7dfdb8e18","tid":310740,"uid":6239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T10:42:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌, 網上資料咩都唔可以盡信架啦on9, 你個腦要黎生草架?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n起碼人地有資料丫, 而且都係大部份可信, 慘撚得過香港人?<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">香港有d乜撚貢獻啊? 出埋d垃圾閃閃旅遊書</span>,<br />\n<br />\n以前我去旅行, 試過有次係高登分享心得資料,<br />\n有幾條on9 (唔係1個, 係幾個)留言問我分享黎做乜,<br />\n有錢賺架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌台狗鳩up都要反思下自己有乜貢獻先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif