f\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e8f84c0216d52741000d87db2d200c76ab16a39","tid":310740,"uid":10319,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T13:21:16.000Z","msg":"樓上有唔少人都on99,乜撚都賴鳩人伏你<br />\n自己唔通唔識睇埋其他網站d食評咩再比較下咩？<br />\n人地覺得好食咪好食囉，又唔係拎支槍指住你去食<br />\n唔通你覺得好食定唔好食佢會收錢？<br />\n人人都有自己對食物既感受，使撚理人地點諗？<br />\n呢樣野連登仔都可以用黎打飛機我真係得啖笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7836697d66de73a0930f296cf3afa42eb344cf3","tid":310740,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T13:21:49.000Z","msg":"佢地算係好易滿足<br />\n好事來既<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n食方面睇多d<br />\n問下連登巴絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a108c92ae773c2e9799902344adee07b0510787f","tid":310740,"uid":83998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T13:24:03.000Z","msg":"真係仲要講到好誇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0180261ca88777c7df2f5e1ae9bc5d18d5da76a","tid":310740,"uid":54510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T14:54:15.000Z","msg":"佢地真係好得閒寫到好詳盡<br />\n景點最中意講一大堆歷史<br />\n野食十次有9次都中大伏"},{"pid":"5ab3bb505e2c41ee38408a901e7bd596fbbc89d3","tid":310740,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T16:24:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢地真係好得閒寫到好詳盡<br />\n景點最中意講一大堆歷史<br />\n野食十次有9次都中大伏</blockquote><br />\n但會繼續寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"913931ce587705649c2e1060ba2d90bd28026d56","tid":310740,"uid":70195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T23:59:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佢地真係好得閒寫到好詳盡<br />\n景點最中意講一大堆歷史<br />\n野食十次有9次都中大伏</blockquote><br />\n但會繼續寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該係要面中過伏都唔出聲，然後繼續寫<br />\n不停loop 更多人中 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09aca2d2e034bbec11051cafc8e21409eeddb796","tid":310740,"uid":8435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T00:58:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>佢地真係好得閒寫到好詳盡<br />\n景點最中意講一大堆歷史<br />\n野食十次有9次都中大伏</blockquote><br />\n但會繼續寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該係要面中過伏都唔出聲，然後繼續寫<br />\n不停loop 更多人中 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好多為賺錢<br />\n出咗名轉做全職旅遊blogger<br />\n大把公司俾埋錢去旅行，又可以出書賺一筆"},{"pid":"19cb9f584476c3f5161cf52eb8059fb04e636865","tid":310740,"uid":73231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T01:10:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用tabelog啦</blockquote><br />\n我見好多餐廳都係 3.2 - 3.8 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好難揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a8014d3c06a66dab0f2bfa66d94903083806c2b","tid":310740,"uid":90166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T01:51:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>用tabelog啦</blockquote><br />\n我見好多餐廳都係 3.2 - 3.8 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好難揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實中下伏有咩好怕～<br />\nTabelog要俾錢先search到全部餐廳，覺得唔夠用"},{"pid":"8535c5fe290b56f7cd8803aaef5852c61bf11ee4","tid":310740,"uid":78252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T01:56:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實支那blog仲可信過台灣人<br />\n好多成日出去玩既支那人都叫有點見識<br />\n不過要忍受簡體字</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢樣真<br />\n支那網資訊多同埋準確得多<br />\n不過殘體囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講漏左<br />\n除左食之外<br />\n食野都係睇番TripAdvisor</blockquote><br />\ntrip advisor 我都覺得唔係好準 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n例如日本菜 可能外國人未食過真正好味嘅日本菜</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁老老豆豆<br />\n假如係意大利<br />\n你想搵好食既日本菜/廣東菜<br />\n<br />\nTripAdvisor 當然可信性低好多<br />\n學你咁講<br />\n<br />\n佢地根本未食過好食既</blockquote><br />\n係歐洲太耐想食日本野，tripadvisor上面話好食既多數未必好食，普通到極，但外國菜就幾可靠"},{"pid":"ff9c843eed582c8b3d54fcd107c2048c9e12a6d9","tid":310740,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T02:45:00.000Z","msg":"台仔食慣垃圾黑心食物,出到去普通野都話好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c96b78ff0ed48f79fd9e1b6ec16a62bc9ec1387d","tid":310740,"uid":48473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T02:52:20.000Z","msg":"依個真<br />\n我淨係睇點樣去啲景點 佢地推薦啲野我好少食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21e15907f0377ca26b143d31754de7d610e67353","tid":310740,"uid":6239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T03:05:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>台仔食慣垃圾黑心食物,出到去普通野都話好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n班窮撚邊有食過好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3acf54dde9584b2e0a4934292d867e81ed8c6ea3","tid":310740,"uid":36510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T03:10:44.000Z","msg":"台仔blog同openrice一樣都係信唔過,<br />\n佢地d口味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試過睇過幾個blog講某間餐廳d野好食唔咸,<br />\n我食過之後覺得咸到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1bccea2ae6bf51215d05281d72794f5dca26726","tid":310740,"uid":73231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T04:29:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>台仔blog同openrice一樣都係信唔過,<br />\n佢地d口味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試過睇過幾個blog講某間餐廳d野好食唔咸,<br />\n我食過之後覺得咸到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你肯定未眼過 yelp 啲鬼佬推介嘅中餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08360fd77dc0126b979559670e84568d77b19ecf","tid":310740,"uid":22287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T11:20:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>用tabelog啦</blockquote><br />\n我見好多餐廳都係 3.2 - 3.8 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好難揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實中下伏有咩好怕～<br />\nTabelog要俾錢先search到全部餐廳，覺得唔夠用</blockquote><br />\n最近先係咁定咩？<br />\n我記得上次睇 , app 同 web 版唔同"},{"pid":"507c35599b8d48ba4538f9ed833cb40667b42727","tid":310740,"uid":37524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T11:51:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓上有唔少人都on99,乜撚都賴鳩人伏你<br />\n自己唔通唔識睇埋其他網站d食評咩再比較下咩？<br />\n人地覺得好食咪好食囉，又唔係拎支槍指住你去食<br />\n唔通你覺得好食定唔好食佢會收錢？<br />\n人人都有自己對食物既感受，使撚理人地點諗？<br />\n呢樣野連登仔都可以用黎打飛機我真係得啖笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n廢話"},{"pid":"3c9379ab56c710e903c1e7aa4798023b23ca333d","tid":310740,"uid":90000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T12:31:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>用tabelog啦</blockquote><br />\n我見好多餐廳都係 3.2 - 3.8 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好難揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實中下伏有咩好怕～<br />\nTabelog要俾錢先search到全部餐廳，覺得唔夠用</blockquote><br />\n最近先係咁定咩？<br />\n我記得上次睇 , app 同 web 版唔同</blockquote><br />\napp版要用日本account download，登記左有30日免費，記得出發前先登記。<br />\n另外tabelog 其實都有好似OpenRice 咁賣好評，都唔可以盡信"},{"pid":"1dc8146442ef2c27328d574fc408c7797ad3e236","tid":310740,"uid":73231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T13:53:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>用tabelog啦</blockquote><br />\n我見好多餐廳都係 3.2 - 3.8 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好難揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實中下伏有咩好怕～<br />\nTabelog要俾錢先search到全部餐廳，覺得唔夠用</blockquote><br />\n最近先係咁定咩？<br />\n我記得上次睇 , app 同 web 版唔同</blockquote><br />\napp版要用日本account download，登記左有30日免費，記得出發前先登記。<br />\n另外tabelog 其實都有好似OpenRice 咁賣好評，都唔可以盡信</blockquote><br />\n我上 jalan 好少旅舘低過 4。啲人基本4 4 5 5。之後睇中要 google 睇其它 site 評價"},{"pid":"f315dbf0101e8d10605b3cb22d8ba2565fec1c2c","tid":310740,"uid":48659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T14:12:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我係歐洲自由行兩個月都係靠台仔台妹blog<br />\n基本上交通可以盡信<br />\n不過唔係站站都有資料<br />\n同行日本仔話日本blog資料仲豐富<br />\n食物方面通常係睇佢地介紹當地特色食物<br />\n有咩必食小吃美食之類<br />\n但餐廳都係會睇google maps既留言（通常都幾準）<br />\n<br />\nBtw 根據同行台妹反應，佢真係乜都會覺得好食<br />\n有次信左台灣blog係Amsterdam 食媽媽餐廳<br />\nTraditional Dutch food<br />\n鹹到仆街仲要成廿歐一個人<br />\n除左鹹之外我咩都食唔出（日本仔同反應）<br />\n但台妹覺得好好食...<br />\n<br />\n有時希望香港人都會寫travel blog</blockquote><br />\n香港人大部分都隨性d 唔鍾意做咁多資料搜集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個個趕頭趕命咁, 點會有心機寫blog<br />\n寧願快快手放哂fb呃like好過啦...</blockquote><br />\n我連影張相擺上網都慳得做啦<br />\n真心佩服去旅行寫埋旅記出黎既人  有咁多時間做呢啲野   不過好事黎既  無人做既話有時連想睇下相關資訊都無"},{"pid":"6973d7e9ae5e42e1f3d0fd6a02efe9545287af7b","tid":310740,"uid":122155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T18:26:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌, 網上資料咩都唔可以盡信架啦on9, 你個腦要黎生草架?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n起碼人地有資料丫, 而且都係大部份可信, 慘撚得過香港人?<br />\n香港有d乜撚貢獻啊? 出埋d垃圾閃閃旅遊書,<br />\n<br />\n以前我去旅行, 試過有次係高登分享心得資料,<br />\n有幾條on9 (唔係1個, 係幾個)留言問我分享黎做乜,<br />\n有錢賺架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n吓 你又陰公啲 啲人把口又係衰嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過講真 寫blog呢樣野台灣人真係有心好多<br />\n香港嘅人口大約有台灣嘅三分之一<br />\n但係blog嘅數量都唔知有冇十分一......"},{"pid":"70f694c18376f738fa12a8558aee5b612cab593e","tid":310740,"uid":96107,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T18:42:06.000Z","msg":"其實細心啲睇，台灣人啲blog既資訊內容十之八九都係互相copy，再自已改小小咁就當新文咁出<br />\n<br />\n有啲根本交通都唔可以信，某啲路線我懷疑佢地根本未撚搭過/路線已經cut左都建議人地搭，佢地都係亂鳩咁係第二個blog到copy返黎，要搵交通資訊其實信google map仲好<br />\n<br />\n野食同景點方面又係伏到hihi，明明好撚普通既都比佢吹到好好食好好玩咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n雖一可取之處就係睇佢地自然景點啲風景相，睇下係咪真係值得去，因為佢地啲相都係亂咁黎，重量不重質，如果佢地影出黎都靚，咁現場應該會靚多幾倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3630ca7cab0ed55711d15f56aa89227a46253ad6","tid":310740,"uid":70293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-07T21:42:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>用tabelog啦</blockquote><br />\n我見好多餐廳都係 3.2 - 3.8 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好難揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中下伏有咩好怕</span></span>～<br />\nTabelog要俾錢先search到全部餐廳，覺得唔夠用</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"521c343f6e02f6eda13ffc11acc1435ea5731832","tid":310740,"uid":62755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-08T02:53:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢地真係好得閒寫到好詳盡<br />\n景點最中意講一大堆歷史<br />\n野食十次有9次都中大伏</blockquote><br />\n佢地最鍾意寫本來乜乜乜，後來改乜乜乜<br />\n爸爸咩感受，bb扭幾耐計，以前未有仔點點點<br />\n通常一篇野頭個十幾行可以全部唔睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}